  "detailed_description": "Race downhill while performing aerial acrobatics in Escargot Kart, the original rolling platformer. Creatively rocket, jump and parachute your way across dozens of virtual physics playgrounds. <br><br>Land a satisfying quadruple backflip or watch your hero somersault downhill after a crash. Unlock more characters and vehicles as you master each world. <br><br>Earn coins for each flip and exchange them for power-ups. Mix and match equipment to jump higher, fly farther and crash harder. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488070/extras/1817606e2207e0752e022c2ede2db94a.avif?t=1568578516\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Complete hundreds of action packed challenges <br></li><li>Unlock and combine equipment to increase your abilities <br></li><li>Earn achievements landing spectacular stunts</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/488070/extras/a2c916064fd56839837730482348c9d0.avif?t=1568578516\" width=610 height=371 /></span>",
